# LLM Wiki Agent — Cursor Workflow Instructions

This wiki is maintained entirely by Cursor Agent. No API key or Node.js scripts needed — just open this repo in Cursor and talk to the agent.

## How to Use

Describe what you want in plain English:
- *"Ingest this file: raw/papers/my-paper.md"*
- *"Ingest all new files"* (batch mode)
- *"What does the wiki say about transformer models?"*
- *"Check the wiki for orphan pages and contradictions"*
- *"Build the knowledge graph"*

Or use shorthand triggers:
- `ingest <file>` → runs the Ingest Workflow (single file)
- `ingest` → runs the Ingest Workflow (batch mode — scan raw/ for new/changed files)
- `query: <question>` → runs the Query Workflow
- `lint` → runs the Lint Workflow
- `build graph` → runs the Graph Workflow

## Wiki Schema

Read `WIKI_SCHEMA.md` at the project root for the full wiki data model (page format, frontmatter, naming conventions, index format).

